gomodel:SYNGO_5150  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 1, 2: PDLIM5 (aka. ENH, Enigma Homolog) and SPAR (Spine-Associated RapGAP, gene SIPA1L1) co-immunoprecipitated and interacted in yeast two-hybrid.\n\nFigure 7: overexpression of PDLIM5a in cultured hippocampal neurons reduced mature mushroom shaped spines and increased thin filopodia-like structures. In contrast, overexpressing PDLIM5b and a PDLIM5a construct lacking LIM domains 2 and 3 caused a significant increase in dendritic spine head size, suggesting that the PDLIM5a overexpression phenotype was conditional on its binding to SPAR. Knockdown of PDLIM5a had the same effect as overexpression of PDLIM5b and PDLIM5a-ΔLIM.\n\nFigure 8: postsynaptic localization of PDLIM5 is increased upon PKC activation in cultured hippocampal neurons at 27DIV.. Experimental description: M&M:\n\"For spine morphology studies, hippocampal primary neuronal cultures prepared from embryonic day (E) 18-19 rat embryos were plated at high density (~750 cells mm-2)\"\n\nantibody:\n\"PDLIM5 antibodies GU8 were produced by immunization of rabbits with pMal-PDLIM5 PDZ domain (Cocalico Biologicals).\"\n\nconstructs:\n\"PDLIM5a, PDLIM5b, and Enigma cDNAs were obtained by PCR from a rat brain Marathon cDNA library using amino- and carboxy-terminus primers and cloned into vector HA-GW1 or myc-GW1. Deletion constructs were generated by PCR with appropriate primers. For PDLIM5 and Enigma deletions in pGAD10, regions are denoted in Fig. 1A. HA-PDLIM5aΔLIM in GW1 lacks aa477-497. Deletions for SPAR-Act2 domain cloned in pBHA were ΔN (aa 1313-1505), ΔNC (aa 1313-1415) and ΔC (1216-1415).\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" ;
        dc:date           "2023-02-25" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_BP_5150" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10116" .

pav:providedBy  a  owl:AnnotationProperty .

